Thanks for pointing that out, @dilyanpalauzov!

Podman and Buildah support the exact same transports for push and pull.  It seems like a doc-only issue.  My proposal would be to point to the `containers-transports` man page instead of listing them in buildah/podman push/pull.

@mtrmac @nalind @TomSweeneyRedHat WDYT?
